{"tid":2287560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《鬼滅》被玩壞!禰豆子尖牙變飛機杯 「淫之呼吸」讓網友傻眼","createTime":"2020-11-16T00:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T01:44:46.000Z","uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf59f554b15a5ecc2efc4dda187fb2a547fe61d","tid":2287560,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/qbkxhw73DR13lsXKXKjfSncEBG0=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OMMKM4OJJNGQ7JECTJOFPLU6HI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqbkxhw73DR13lsXKXKjfSncEBG0%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOMMKM4OJJNGQ7JECTJOFPLU6HI.jpg&h=c19b9342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超人氣動漫《鬼滅之刃》的首部電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版：無限列車篇》橫掃票房，不但AV片商推出AV版《鬼滅之刃》，連情趣用品業者也看準了這波熱潮，推出女主角禰豆子嘴部造型的飛機杯，尖牙形態讓網友看傻眼，直呼「廠商有病」、「陰牙人：抗議她學我」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/HwRxviM_5A586U2IuuBYA7R-qxE=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LH2SGMOKERANLHVEFL7D3J5DVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHwRxviM_5A586U2IuuBYA7R-qxE%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLH2SGMOKERANLHVEFL7D3J5DVU.jpg&h=5557b63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這款命名為「鬼滅之八重齒」的飛機杯，以禰豆子做為封面，模擬禰豆子在動漫中被鬼咬過後生出尖牙的嘴部形態，標榜逼真重建嘴部的真實情況，還有一個極具彈性的舌頭，宣傳標語也致敬《鬼滅之刃》寫到，「全注入！淫之呼吸！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/VsRveqKa1tLbIKKBkN2PRl1sp1U=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DD2OQ37BPJHAZJ7VMTBYLEB4EA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVsRveqKa1tLbIKKBkN2PRl1sp1U%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDD2OQ37BPJHAZJ7VMTBYLEB4EA.jpg&h=e6924235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這款飛機杯本月上市後隨即成為熱門商品，不少銷售18禁商品的業者將它和AV版《鬼滅之刃》放在一起宣傳販賣。也有業者在推特上將實際商品拍照秀給網友看，引發許多迴響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/iuGVXgVDnE0i90gNDdQlCWkaF_Q=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IT7KLNSXSZFE3IT3LGGCYTPD7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiuGVXgVDnE0i90gNDdQlCWkaF_Q%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIT7KLNSXSZFE3IT3LGGCYTPD7I.jpg&h=974e617b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣網友也在PTT討論留言「但是被牙齒碰到其實很不舒服」、「拿來夾核桃」、「開發者：前水柱鱗瀧左近次」、「這種一看就本體是賣外盒的」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/VD3xANGpr8-LoDwa237kWEltqXE=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QSYHSOHAPZE5JBADUIXDSASJEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVD3xANGpr8-LoDwa237kWEltqXE%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQSYHSOHAPZE5JBADUIXDSASJEA.jpg&h=5e6fa4b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbbcbefb8cc831eefab7c0bb1ed294bb74f22e0e","tid":2287560,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"上三悠亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a337dd9e995e2950109c0c164ee721f62863c9","tid":2287560,"uid":32577,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCQb4CH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCQb4CH.jpg&h=e82c69d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢隻好過啦"},{"pid":"7e3551e506074ea53f46404066a852586626f97e","tid":2287560,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"40a337dd9e995e2950109c0c164ee721f62863c9","tid":2287560,"uid":32577,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCQb4CH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCQb4CH.jpg&h=e82c69d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢隻好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"三藏..."},{"pid":"aa291537e074a0838668d920301d61bec1f90c6f","tid":2287560,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892c5efa3a8cdb36e4fe8faf64c285ac63e3c08b","tid":2287560,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2cebb577d865d8030b8231ffb5f45674ed6cbe","tid":2287560,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}